CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper August 9, 1947, pg. 18, and August 16, 1947, pg. 16. reads: " 'Night of Stars' Greatest Show in Frogs' History - Scenes from night of stars - The Syria Mosque in Pittsburgh was packed to the rafters Monday night for the Frogs' "Night of Stars."...Judge Henry Ellenbogen of Pittsburgh receives a check from Bill Robinson for the Negro College Fund..."
TitMainTitle: Judge Henry Ellenbogen receiving check from Bill "Bojangles" Robinson for the Negro College Fund, for Night of Stars
